Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西…像沟口先生那样做就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 有模有样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从1200单位距离开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇定下来 配合呼吸的节奏哦 小姑娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次打中之后再拉远200单位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中率维持在90%以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前距离 2800单位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你的眼光挺准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实战的情况还不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这孩子挺有天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好锻炼锻炼 让她单人狙击也不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为Alivs头号狙击手的潜力简直是满分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这机体我开不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神剑型的驾驶员拥有特殊的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适合他们的机体是凭此决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是这部Mk.Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一骑的同步率已经高到无法接纳他人的协同代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑真好命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的机体要是也能给这么改造一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去求求新联合国呗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们帮你改造好了 再一下子抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点用这家伙把远见给同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这机体里装了三倍的芬里尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为的就是能炸得一干二净 什么也不留下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种机体 你们也不会想开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个未知数 不应该投入实战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士你害怕把她加入系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一骑和真矢都陷入危险了 你会先救谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没去看真矢训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在今天之内把这份文件处理好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「岛民在俗称盂兰盆会或盂兰盆节的节日中的行动概要」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了就是盂兰盆祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候了还祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为是这时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛是为了保护「和平」这种文化而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈妹妹 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈可帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令也说能够马上上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够马上上战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把资料发给你 你帮我向各部门确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 为什么还需要驾驶员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者在各地活化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方也不知道什么时候会被大举进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我当然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 今天一定要把那事办了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢又出了这档子事 我家都乱成一锅粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一想到真矢要驾驶法芙娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 明明大家也都是强装镇定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正害怕的是孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大人表现出不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会给孩子们造成不必要的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也挺顽强的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了之前那个岛的资料和他的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了延续驾驶员生命的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们未来的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明你和你的女儿都具备出色的洞察彼岸的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的努力 一定会有回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你没事吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好多沟口先生转来转去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你来得正好 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为协同代码的影响 醉成烂泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉成烂泥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家没醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是新手激昂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.22,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,1000)}beginner's high
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是因为第一次训练紧张坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 接下来就交给你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她将来可是你重要的战友 好好把人家送回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到一骑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远 远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 总士 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 总士和乙姬 你们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我正忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就负起责任来送远见回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我这个战斗指挥官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 乙姬 回头见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士你真是不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个问题的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论面临怎样的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要保护齐格飞系统内的所有驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不是一个人在承受 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧 远见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该能自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 感觉好像飘飘然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次下来的时候 走路也是东倒西歪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了和大家一样的景色的那种喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子的心情肯定也是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种感觉 与其说是驾驶法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说是成为了法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是变成了另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会改变的 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎么提着这么多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庆祝你训练归来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑要不要也一起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天爸爸会回来 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 叫上真壁司令也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢 我去联系看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 姐姐你要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了别问了 在妈妈回来之前快做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛 你就当是帮我个忙呗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑手艺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他没有妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你反正做菜特别糟糕 不如跟他一块儿住？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我又不是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话妈妈也会承认我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些派出去当主力 然后来个侧面攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！敌人来得比预料的还快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就要干脆利落地出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您回来 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说一骑在这儿叨扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你经常来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你在想什么啊 弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装啦 明明就自己也偷着乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就只有在真壁叔叔面前会示弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餐具洗好了 还有其他命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 要不要来杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不给我命令的话 我会很为难 不知道该做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就尽管为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个高难度的任务…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得准备给爸爸过去世后的第一次盂兰盆节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量多杀敌 这样才能告慰爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天弓子真是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去这么多年 我又回想起了建造这个岛的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我这么说很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有人想在岛上开始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生和弓子都是值得信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请你支持孩子们的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这顿晚饭真够重大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是觉得有些事情是一直不会变的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也要跳盂兰盆会舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建起高台 大家一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有各种摊点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是舞会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点不一样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是祭奠死者的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安魂弥撒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 类似这种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得帮藏前和翔子准备一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 那甲洋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢 蠢材 甲洋还活着吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我没救成的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再一起去看望他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起跟他说话的话 他肯定会醒的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里不行 不能去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门发出应答 Ambivalent 类型无法断定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标…未被识别成敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 防御幕墙启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让所有驾驶员登上法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门不认为是敌人…难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是这样 那可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会有驾驶员遇害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机配置到各个方位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Mk.Ⅶ携带上次的装备待在中央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让远见…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要足够的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会遭受和摩尔多瓦同等的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让这种事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想在我的岛上胡做非为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五个方位遭到同时进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机前往指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时应战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到达指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太突然了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就看着吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没问题吧 真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会接通音频通讯 便于你把握战况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你要听从我的指示射击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人正在同化重力波防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布伦希尔德系统启动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始自主防御
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那个类型的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来了？是被打倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了个少见的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得小心点 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机使用配备的火器应战 千万别靠近敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…没有攻过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃癸斯护盾解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅴ 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅷ 在同化行动中消灭它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！干掉它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛！所有人瞄准头部的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的 太不搭调了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9点钟方向 1点钟方向 6点钟方向的敌人均已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3点钟方向的敌人撤向空中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要漏掉一只 岛就会被吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没子弹了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅲ 快住手！撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人接触到Mk.Ⅲ了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有机体都前去支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 妈妈！妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把驾驶员弹出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我连咲良一起打吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到达现场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准敌人停止动作的瞬间 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别动手 坏人我来当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不是这个岛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想杀咲良吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冻结Mk.Ⅷ的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良！咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}救我！救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你宁愿我们所有人都被同化吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他们 卡农！快打！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛锁住我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是动手 敌人就会冲着你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 我们会把敌人从Mk.Ⅲ身边引开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后怎么做交给你处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引开？要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点Mk.Ⅶ会处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说远见…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一只
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员全员平安无事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见前辈…真的太厉害了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部机体撤回向岛船坞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家去迎接驾驶员们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕…好害怕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你回来 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…现在才后怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吃饭吧 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能别对我直呼其名了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是你哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这没关系 总士就是总士
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因祭典而喧嚣的龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭奠的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不磨灭的音容笑貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 苍穹的法芙娜 第二十回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯火 -浮灯-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
